1070
01:09:45,948 --> 01:09:48,583
[WOMAN SHRIEKS]

1071
01:09:48,585 --> 01:09:50,885
<i>- GET OFF, GET OFF!
- [SLAPS]</i>

1072
01:09:50,887 --> 01:09:52,287
<i>GET OFF!</i>

1073
01:09:54,156 --> 01:09:56,291
[DAISY SHUDDERING]

1074
01:09:59,261 --> 01:10:01,763
[WHISPERING]
GET UP. QUICK, GET UP.

1075
01:10:01,765 --> 01:10:03,531
WE NEED TO MOVE NOW.

1076
01:10:06,035 --> 01:10:08,736
- WHAT'S GOING ON?
- SHH.

1077
01:10:23,319 --> 01:10:25,853
[SOFT CREAKING]

1078
01:10:28,224 --> 01:10:30,425
DAISY.
[PANTING]

1079
01:10:30,427 --> 01:10:33,127
[GRUNTS]
I'M TIRED.

1080
01:10:33,129 --> 01:10:35,396
MY FEET HURT.

1081
01:10:36,632 --> 01:10:39,234
I NEED WATER!

1082
01:10:39,236 --> 01:10:42,003
WE'VE BEEN WALKING
FOR HOURS.

1083
01:10:42,005 --> 01:10:43,738
I'M TIRED.

1084
01:10:43,740 --> 01:10:47,609
- DAISY.
- WILL YOU SHUT UP?! I AM SO SICK

1085
01:10:47,611 --> 01:10:51,246
OF YOUR STUPID,
WHINY VOICE ALL THE TIME.

1086
01:10:51,248 --> 01:10:53,114
<i>DO YOU WANT ME TO JUST
LEAVE YOU HERE?</i>

1087
01:10:53,116 --> 01:10:54,949
<i>BECAUSE THAT'S WHAT
I'M GONNA DO.</i>

1088
01:10:54,951 --> 01:10:56,985
IF YOU DON'T
SHUT THE FUCK UP,

1089
01:10:56,987 --> 01:10:59,687
I AM GONNA RUN AND YOU'RE GONNA
BE LEFT HERE ON YOUR OWN

1090
01:10:59,689 --> 01:11:02,190
<i>IN THE DARK AND YOU'RE
GONNA DIE OUT HERE.</i>

1091
01:11:02,192 --> 01:11:05,326
DO YOU WANNA SEE
YOUR BROTHERS AGAIN?

1092
01:11:06,829 --> 01:11:08,496
WELL, COME ON.

1093
01:11:14,303 --> 01:11:16,004
[SNIFFLING]

1094
01:11:22,811 --> 01:11:25,046
[STREAM RUSHING]

1095
01:11:27,916 --> 01:11:29,517
[PIPER GASPS]

1096
01:11:32,655 --> 01:11:34,822
PIPER.

1097
01:11:34,824 --> 01:11:36,357
PIPER!
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

1098
01:11:36,359 --> 01:11:38,159
IT MIGHT BE POISON.

1099
01:11:38,161 --> 01:11:40,428
- I FORGOT!
- WELL, YOU CAN'T FORGET, OKAY?

1100
01:11:40,430 --> 01:11:42,830
IF YOU DON'T KNOW THE SOURCE,
YOU CAN'T TRUST THE WATER.

1101
01:11:42,832 --> 01:11:46,200
AND YOU SHOULDN'T HAVE EATEN ALL
THAT CHOCOLATE. THAT WAS STUPID.

1102
01:11:46,202 --> 01:11:49,070
MOMMY SAYS I'M A MONSTER
FOR CHOCOLATES.

1103
01:11:50,105 --> 01:11:51,973
I JUST CAN'T HELP MYSELF.

1104
01:11:54,743 --> 01:11:57,812
MAYBE THAT'S WHY
SHE WENT AWAY.

1105
01:11:57,814 --> 01:11:59,113
WHAT?

1106
01:11:59,115 --> 01:12:01,616
'CAUSE I WAS GREEDY.

1107
01:12:01,618 --> 01:12:03,484
[SIGHS]
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

1108
01:12:03,486 --> 01:12:06,387
'CAUSE SHE DIDN'T WANT
TO BE AROUND ME ANYMORE!

1109
01:12:09,091 --> 01:12:12,660
<i>[BIRDS PECKING, CHIRPING]</i>

1110
01:12:13,729 --> 01:12:16,297
HEY.

1111
01:12:16,299 --> 01:12:18,866
SOMETIMES PEOPLE SAY
THINGS THEY DON'T MEAN.

1112
01:12:20,069 --> 01:12:22,070
YOUR MOM LOVES YOU
MORE THAN ANYTHING.

1113
01:12:23,172 --> 01:12:25,273
AND SHE'S
SO PROUD OF YOU.

1114
01:12:25,275 --> 01:12:27,875
- I KNOW THAT FOR A FACT.
- HOW?

1115
01:12:30,179 --> 01:12:33,081
WELL, I'M OLDER
THAN YOU AND...

1116
01:12:35,284 --> 01:12:37,452
IT'S JUST SOMETHING I KNOW.

1117
01:12:38,454 --> 01:12:40,421
AND LISTEN,
ABOUT LAST NIGHT,

1118
01:12:40,423 --> 01:12:44,425
I'M SORRY I SAID THAT STUFF.
I DIDN'T MEAN IT, OKAY?

1119
01:12:47,763 --> 01:12:48,963
COME ON.

1120
01:13:07,816 --> 01:13:09,083
[GRUNTS]

1121
01:13:11,053 --> 01:13:12,420
[YELPS]

1122
01:13:24,933 --> 01:13:27,535
<i>[PIPER SINGING]
♪ NOT BECAUSE THEY'RE DIRTY</i>

1123
01:13:27,537 --> 01:13:29,370
<i>♪ NOT BECAUSE
THEY'RE CLEAN ♪</i>

1124
01:13:29,372 --> 01:13:33,207
♪ NOT BECAUSE I KISSED
A BOY BEHIND A MAGAZINE ♪

1125
01:13:33,209 --> 01:13:36,310
♪ BOYS, BOYS,
HAVING ALL THE FUN ♪

1126
01:13:36,312 --> 01:13:38,980
♪ SHE CAN EVEN
DO THE SPLITS ♪

1127
01:13:38,982 --> 01:13:40,515
♪ BUT I BET YOU 10 BUCKS

1128
01:13:40,517 --> 01:13:42,550
♪ SHE CAN'T DO THIS.

1129
01:13:45,888 --> 01:13:47,455
- DAISY?
- HMM?

1130
01:13:47,457 --> 01:13:49,690
WHAT WAS
YOUR MOMMY LIKE?

1131
01:13:51,126 --> 01:13:53,327
I NEVER REALLY MET HER.

1132
01:13:53,329 --> 01:13:54,662
HOW COME?

1133
01:13:56,131 --> 01:13:58,566
SHE DIED
WHILE I WAS BEING BORN.

1134
01:14:02,871 --> 01:14:04,505
DO YOU MISS HER?

1135
01:14:05,808 --> 01:14:07,208
YEAH,

1136
01:14:07,210 --> 01:14:08,743
SOMETIMES.

1137
01:14:10,846 --> 01:14:13,614
IF SHE'D NEVER HAD ME,
SHE'D PROBABLY STILL BE ALIVE.

1138
01:14:17,986 --> 01:14:19,320
<i>HEY, COME ON.</i>

1139
01:14:19,322 --> 01:14:20,822
WE'VE GOT WALKING TO DO.

1140
01:14:23,959 --> 01:14:25,626
I HATE WALKING.

1141
01:14:28,530 --> 01:14:31,566
WHEN I GET HOME, I'M NEVER
GOING TO WALK AGAIN.

1142
01:14:39,808 --> 01:14:43,177
[SPLASHES]

1143
01:14:46,515 --> 01:14:49,217
LOOK. LOOK!

1144
01:14:50,619 --> 01:14:52,887
THAT'S THE BOYS' PLACE.

1145
01:14:52,889 --> 01:14:56,357
GATESFIELD. THAT'S WHERE
THEY'VE TAKEN EDDIE AND ISAAC.

1146
01:14:56,359 --> 01:14:59,193
I TOLD YOU,
THEY'VE GONE HOME ALREADY.

1147
01:14:59,195 --> 01:15:00,862
BUT YOU'RE NOT SURE.

1148
01:15:01,897 --> 01:15:04,298
<i>JUST 'CAUSE
YOU HAD A DREAM,</i>

1149
01:15:04,300 --> 01:15:06,067
WHO SAYS
THE DREAM'S REAL?

1150
01:15:12,774 --> 01:15:14,342
OKAY,

1151
01:15:14,344 --> 01:15:16,244
COME ON.

1152
01:15:16,246 --> 01:15:17,745
YES. COME ON.

1153
01:15:17,747 --> 01:15:20,014
AS SOON AS I SEE
EDDIE AND ISAAC,

1154
01:15:20,016 --> 01:15:22,683
I'M GONNA GIVE THEM
A BIG HUG. AH.

1155
01:15:27,456 --> 01:15:30,024
<i>[WIND GUSTING]</i>

1156
01:15:34,863 --> 01:15:36,998
[WHISPERING]
WHERE IS EVERYONE?

1157
01:15:38,267 --> 01:15:40,434
<i>- [SHRIEKS]
- [WIND GUSTS]</i>

1158
01:15:40,436 --> 01:15:42,303
PIPER:
WHAT WAS THAT?

1159
01:15:43,539 --> 01:15:45,273
<i>[SHRIEKS]</i>

1160
01:15:47,476 --> 01:15:49,310
[PANTS]

1161
01:15:51,146 --> 01:15:53,147
STAY HERE, OKAY?

1162
01:16:07,863 --> 01:16:10,631
<i>- [METAL CLANGS]
- [WIND BLOWING]</i>

1163
01:16:23,979 --> 01:16:26,113
<i>[STATIC BUZZING]</i>

1164
01:16:36,592 --> 01:16:39,193
<i>- [RADIO CRACKLES]
- [GARBLED SPEECH]</i>

1165
01:17:04,753 --> 01:17:06,754
[FOXES PANTING]

1166
01:17:20,569 --> 01:17:22,069
[BREATHES SHARPLY]

1167
01:17:32,814 --> 01:17:34,882
<i>[THINKING]
ARE YOU HERE?</i>

1168
01:17:37,519 --> 01:17:39,320
<i>YOU'D BETTER NOT BE HERE.</i>

1169
01:19:10,545 --> 01:19:14,849
<i>[DAISY'S VOICE WHISPERING]</i>

1170
01:19:14,851 --> 01:19:16,650
<i>...SYMPATHY OF OTHERS.</i>

1171
01:19:16,652 --> 01:19:18,486
<i>ITCHING, RASHES,
WATER TABLETS.</i>

1172
01:19:18,488 --> 01:19:20,755
<i>CERTAIN DEGREE OF WILLPOWER
AND SELF-DISCIPLINE.</i>

1173
01:19:20,757 --> 01:19:22,556
<i>[HAWK SCREECHES]</i>

1174
01:19:22,558 --> 01:19:25,059
<i>[MUFFLED RUMBLING]</i>

1175
01:19:34,736 --> 01:19:37,037
[SILENT]

1176
01:19:38,173 --> 01:19:39,807
[COUGHS]

1177
01:19:39,809 --> 01:19:42,076
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

1178
01:19:45,313 --> 01:19:46,914
<i>[FOOTSTEPS]</i>

1179
01:19:51,419 --> 01:19:53,821
- WHAT WAS IN THERE?
- COME ON.

1180
01:19:53,823 --> 01:19:56,023
WE NEED TO GET AWAY
FROM HERE.

1181
01:19:57,893 --> 01:19:59,794
WHERE ARE MY BROTHERS?

1182
01:20:01,363 --> 01:20:02,830
I DON'T KNOW.

1183
01:20:05,600 --> 01:20:07,001
COME ON.

1184
01:20:35,764 --> 01:20:38,365
[SNIFFLING]

1185
01:20:54,449 --> 01:20:56,016
<i>[LEAVES RUSTLING]</i>

1186
01:20:57,853 --> 01:20:59,553
<i>[DAISY CRYING]</i>

1187
01:20:59,555 --> 01:21:01,455
EDDIE.

1188
01:21:03,358 --> 01:21:04,959
ARE YOU OKAY?

1189
01:21:10,966 --> 01:21:13,601
CAN YOU JUST GIVE ME A SIGN

1190
01:21:13,603 --> 01:21:15,236
OR SOMETHING?

1191
01:21:19,708 --> 01:21:21,442
EDDIE?

1192
01:21:46,668 --> 01:21:48,135
AHH.

1193
01:21:53,208 --> 01:21:55,609
DAISY: DON'T WORRY.
IT'S NOT FAR NOW.

1194
01:21:56,878 --> 01:21:58,545
WE SHOULD BE HOME
TOMORROW.

1195
01:21:58,547 --> 01:22:00,214
REALLY?

1196
01:22:02,584 --> 01:22:04,451
<i>[WINGS FLAPPING]</i>

1197
01:22:06,221 --> 01:22:08,622
I'VE SAVED A PIECE OF CHOCOLATE.
DO YOU WANT IT NOW?

1198
01:22:10,392 --> 01:22:11,558
<i>[UNZIPS]</i>

1199
01:22:17,332 --> 01:22:19,133
<i>[BRANCH SNAPS]</i>

1200
01:22:31,579 --> 01:22:32,680
QUICK.

1201
01:22:33,782 --> 01:22:35,950
GO! QUICK.

1202
01:22:39,854 --> 01:22:41,488
[PANTING]

1203
01:22:47,595 --> 01:22:49,463
COME ON, PIPER!
COME ON!

1204
01:22:51,766 --> 01:22:53,300
COME ON.

1205
01:22:53,302 --> 01:22:54,368
QUICK.

1206
01:22:59,841 --> 01:23:01,709
- COME ON!
- [PANTING]

1207
01:23:06,314 --> 01:23:07,715
<i>COME ON.</i>

1208
01:23:09,317 --> 01:23:10,651
HURRY UP.

1209
01:23:13,521 --> 01:23:14,722
COME ON.

1210
01:23:18,626 --> 01:23:19,727
IN HERE.

1211
01:23:19,729 --> 01:23:21,261
QUICK.

1212
01:23:21,263 --> 01:23:23,163
[PANTING]

1213
01:23:43,918 --> 01:23:46,186
[SHRIEKING]

1214
01:23:47,789 --> 01:23:49,356
OH, YOU'RE A BIG RABBIT,
AREN'T YOU?

1215
01:23:49,358 --> 01:23:51,225
- PIPER: GET OFF OF ME!
- [MEN LAUGH] HEY.

1216
01:23:51,227 --> 01:23:53,927
- NO! GET OFF!
- I'M NOT GOING TO HURT YOU.

1217
01:23:53,929 --> 01:23:56,230
- HEY.
- LET HER GO!

1218
01:23:57,198 --> 01:23:58,966
I SAID
LET HER GO NOW!

1219
01:23:58,968 --> 01:24:00,367
[LAUGHING]

1220
01:24:00,369 --> 01:24:02,202
WHAT THE FUCK
ARE YOU LAUGHING AT?

1221
01:24:03,038 --> 01:24:04,872
DON'T MOVE ANY CLOSER.

1222
01:24:04,874 --> 01:24:07,307
WE'RE ONLY WINDING
YOU UP, LOVE, EH?

1223
01:24:08,810 --> 01:24:10,344
COME ON, LITTLE LADY.

1224
01:24:11,546 --> 01:24:13,047
IT'S JUST A BIT OF FUN.

1225
01:24:14,916 --> 01:24:16,583
<i>DON'T YOU DARE!</i>

1226
01:24:19,687 --> 01:24:22,056
TAKE IT EASY NOW.
TAKE IT EASY. TAKE IT EASY.

1227
01:24:22,058 --> 01:24:23,590
<i>CALM DOWN.
TAKE IT EASY.</i>

1228
01:24:23,592 --> 01:24:25,492
<i>- YOU DON'T HAVE TO DO ANY--
- [GUNSHOT]</i>

1229
01:24:25,494 --> 01:24:27,261
<i>[DAISY'S VOICE WHISPERING]
FIND A GOAL IN LIFE.</i>

1230
01:24:27,263 --> 01:24:28,929
<i>THEY STAY IN. STOP.
WHAT IS YOUR PROBLEM?</i>

1231
01:24:28,931 --> 01:24:31,031
<i>[ECHOING]
WHAT IS YOUR PROBLEM?</i>

1232
01:24:31,033 --> 01:24:32,866
<i>HURRY THE FUCK UP.
STAY AWAY FROM DISTRACTIONS.</i>

1233
01:24:32,868 --> 01:24:35,803
<i>TAKE RISKS.
STEP OUT OF YOUR-- SHE ALMOST GOT--</i>

1234
01:24:37,405 --> 01:24:40,007
<i>ACCEPT LIFE IS UNFAIR.
FOCUS ON YOUR GOAL.</i>

1235
01:24:40,009 --> 01:24:43,877
- OH GOD! [MOANING]
- THAT'S FOR TOUCHING MY COUSIN

1236
01:24:43,879 --> 01:24:46,980
WITH YOUR DIRTY,
DISGUSTING FINGERS!

1237
01:24:46,982 --> 01:24:49,183
<i>- [MOANING]
- [DAISY PANTING]</i>

1238
01:25:11,673 --> 01:25:13,740
<i>[WIND WHOOSHING]</i>

1239
01:25:17,212 --> 01:25:19,313
- [UNZIPPING]
- THE MAP.

1240
01:25:19,315 --> 01:25:20,347
MAP.

1241
01:25:21,716 --> 01:25:23,851
THE COMPASS.

1242
01:25:23,853 --> 01:25:25,819
[MUTTERS]
THE MAP.

1243
01:25:25,821 --> 01:25:27,888
THE MAP. OH SHIT.

1244
01:25:30,225 --> 01:25:32,493
<i>[BIRD CAWING]</i>

1245
01:25:34,395 --> 01:25:36,163
<i>[ZIPS]</i>

1246
01:25:43,171 --> 01:25:45,139
I DON'T KNOW
WHERE WE ARE.

1247
01:26:55,810 --> 01:26:58,245
THIS SEEMS LIKE
A NICE PLACE.

1248
01:26:59,180 --> 01:27:01,215
WHY DON'T WE JUST STAY HERE?

1249
01:27:02,217 --> 01:27:03,650
<i>[SIGHS]</i>

1250
01:27:04,719 --> 01:27:05,852
OKAY.

1251
01:27:12,660 --> 01:27:15,128
IT DOESN'T MATTER
IF WE JUST...

1252
01:27:15,130 --> 01:27:16,863
STAY HERE.

1253
01:27:34,682 --> 01:27:36,617
[HAWK SCREECHES]

1254
01:27:40,888 --> 01:27:42,689
<i>[SCREECHING]</i>

1255
01:27:51,633 --> 01:27:54,268
IT'S EDDIE'S HAWK.
LOOK.

1256
01:27:59,707 --> 01:28:00,707
COME ON.

1257
01:28:01,743 --> 01:28:02,876
COME ON.

1258
01:28:08,816 --> 01:28:10,317
[SCREECHING]

1259
01:28:11,853 --> 01:28:13,787
IT'S TAKING US HOME.

1260
01:28:13,789 --> 01:28:15,255
I TOLD YOU, DIDN'T I?

1261
01:28:15,257 --> 01:28:16,823
EDDIE'S HOME.

1262
01:28:17,859 --> 01:28:19,660
[SCREECHING]

1263
01:28:50,024 --> 01:28:52,025
[PIPER GASPS]

1264
01:28:53,261 --> 01:28:55,362
[PIPER GRUNTS]

1265
01:29:22,824 --> 01:29:23,990
[POTTERY CLATTERS]

1266
01:29:35,069 --> 01:29:37,637
<i>[FLIES BUZZING]</i>

1267
01:29:53,521 --> 01:29:55,689
MAYBE THEY'RE
AT THE BARN.

1268
01:30:10,405 --> 01:30:11,605
<i>DAISY:
EDDIE?</i>

1269
01:30:13,141 --> 01:30:15,008
<i>[THUNKS]</i>

1270
01:30:15,010 --> 01:30:17,277
[JET WHIMPERING]

1271
01:30:17,279 --> 01:30:18,912
PIPER:
JET!

1272
01:30:18,914 --> 01:30:21,014
JET.
DAISY, IT'S JET.

1273
01:30:21,016 --> 01:30:24,017
<i>- OH, JET!
- [DOG WHINES]</i>

1274
01:30:24,019 --> 01:30:25,419
OH, I LOVE YOU, JET.

1275
01:30:25,421 --> 01:30:27,687
[LAUGHS]

1276
01:30:29,223 --> 01:30:31,124
<i>LOOK AT ME, JET.</i>

1277
01:30:31,126 --> 01:30:32,325
YOU'RE BLEEDING.

1278
01:30:32,327 --> 01:30:34,528
WHAT HAPPENED?
LOOK AT ME.

1279
01:30:35,763 --> 01:30:37,931
AND I WILL NEVER
LET YOU GO.

1280
01:30:47,675 --> 01:30:49,910
[SILENT]

1281
01:31:30,017 --> 01:31:32,853
<i>[RUSTLING]</i>

1282
01:31:50,304 --> 01:31:52,806
<i>[PIPER EATING]</i>

1283
01:32:06,320 --> 01:32:09,689
<i>[JET BARKING]</i>

1284
01:32:15,162 --> 01:32:16,863
WHAT'S UP WITH HIM?

1285
01:32:19,233 --> 01:32:21,201
<i>[BARKING CONTINUES]</i>

1286
01:32:25,172 --> 01:32:26,640
HE'S IN THE WOODS.

1287
01:32:27,475 --> 01:32:28,975
<i>DAISY!</i>

1288
01:32:28,977 --> 01:32:30,277
<i>DAISY, BE CAREFUL!</i>

1289
01:32:30,279 --> 01:32:31,912
<i>[BARKING CONTINUES]</i>

1290
01:32:41,589 --> 01:32:43,823
<i>[LOUDER BARKING]</i>

1291
01:32:47,361 --> 01:32:48,728
[JET WHINING]

1292
01:33:13,421 --> 01:33:15,322
[GASPS]

1293
01:33:18,025 --> 01:33:19,626
EDDIE?

1294
01:33:20,494 --> 01:33:21,962
CAN YOU HEAR ME?

1295
01:33:25,066 --> 01:33:26,333
EDDIE.

1296
01:33:27,368 --> 01:33:29,035
I NEED YOU.

1297
01:33:29,037 --> 01:33:30,236
PLEASE.

1298
01:33:31,939 --> 01:33:34,007
I LOVE YOU.

1299
01:33:34,009 --> 01:33:35,909
PLEASE.

1300
01:33:36,944 --> 01:33:38,345
[SOBBING]

1301
01:33:38,347 --> 01:33:40,113
[MOANS]

1302
01:33:40,115 --> 01:33:41,615
EDDIE?

1303
01:33:41,617 --> 01:33:43,316
- [EXHALES]
- IT'S ME.

1304
